channel.title: CVE Feed for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Deploy WebLogic Plugin
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Deploy WebLogic Plugin

item.title: CVE-2019-10464|2024-08-04T22:24:18.596Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20deploy%20weblogic%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery vulnerability in Jenkins Deploy WebLogic Plugin allows attackers to connect to an attacker-specified URL using attacker-specified credentials, or determine whether a file or directory with an attacker-specified path exists on the Jenkins master file system.

item.title: CVE-2019-10465|2024-08-04T22:24:18.548Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20deploy%20weblogic%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Deploy WebLogic Plugin allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to connect to an attacker-specified URL using attacker-specified credentials, or determine whether a file or directory with an attacker-specified path exists on the Jenkins master file system.
